      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "And to just save the reader double checking this, because it&#39;s hard to verify by testing, the <code>keySet()</code> method effectively returns a LinkedHashSet which reflects the order of your <code>put()</code> calls. Note that repeated calls to <code>put()</code> for the same key will not change the order unless you <code>remove()</code> the key beforehand."
