      "body" : "To use TreeMap it required that key class have to implement Comparable interface. If not, then some kind of RuntimeException will be thrown. TreeMap it&#39;s also sorted map, but I think author want to use just ordered (not sorted) map. LinkedHashMap it&#39;s good choice to get only ordered map (as You said, &quot;determined by insertion order&quot;)."
